column2: SELECT TOP # p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, str (p.u - p.g, #, #) as ugModelColor, str (p.g - p.r, #, #) as grModelColor, str (p.r - p.i, #, #) as riModelColor, str (p.i - p.z, #, #) as izModelColor, dbo.fIAUFromEq (p.ra, p.[dec]) as SDSSname, p.cModelMag_g, p.cModelMag_i, p.cModelMag_r, p.cModelMag_z FROM BESTDR8..Star AS p JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID = p.objID JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id WHERE p.r > # AND p.r < # AND (p.flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags (#) ) > #) ORDER BY x.up_id
